<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>頁面不存在</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <div class="container">
        <h1>🔍 找不到頁面</h1>
      </div>
    </header>
    
    <div class="container">
      <div class="not-found-section">
        <h2>404 - 頁面不存在</h2>
        <p>您要查找的頁面不存在或已被移動。</p>
        <p class="url-info">請求的網址：<code><%= url %></code></p>
        
        <div class="actions">
          <a href="/" class="btn">🛒 前往購物</a>
          <a href="/admin" class="btn">⚙️ 管理後台</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <style>
      .not-found-section {
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 3rem;
        margin: 2rem 0;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        border-left: 4px solid #2196F3;
      }
      
      .url-info {
        background: #f0f8ff;
        border: 1px solid #e3f2fd;
        padding: 1rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin: 1rem 0;
        word-break: break-all;
      }
      
      .actions {
        margin: 2rem 0;
      }
      
      .actions .btn {
        margin: 0 0.5rem;
        display: inline-block;
      }
    </style>
  </body>
</html>